ith-on-itikaf-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":27681,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on I&#8217;tikaf: The Prophet&#8217;s spiritual retreat in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would seek spiritual retreat in the mosque\u00a0during the last ten nights of Ramadan, until Allah Almighty caused him to pass away. His wives continued to perform the retreat after him. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2026, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1172 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28484,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/29\/itikaf-ramadan-last-ten\/","url_meta":{"origin":27681,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet secludes himself in the last ten nights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 29, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would retreat to the mosque in the last ten nights of Ramadan. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2025, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1171 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/prophet-revises-quran-itikaf\/","url_meta":{"origin":27681,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet reviews the Quran in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would review the Quran once every year in Ramadan, and he reviewed it twice in the year he passed away. The Prophet would retreat in the mosque for ten days every year, and he secluded himself for twenty days\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/worship-jihad-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":27681,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet strives in last ten nights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the last ten nights of Ramadan arrived, the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would tighten his belt, spend the night in worship, and awaken his family. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2024, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1174 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteo